==Galician==
[[File:Cemiterio de Santo Amaro - Pondal.jpg|thumb|''Aqui jaz o cantor da raza galega Eduardo Pondal. Finou en VIII de marzo ano MCMXVII'' ("Here lies the singer of the Galician race, Eduardo Pondal. He ended March 8, 1917").]]
===Etymology===
From Old Galician and {{inh|gl|roa-opt|jazer}} (13th century, ''{{w|Cantigas de Santa Maria}}''), from {{inh|gl|VL.|iaceo|iacere}}. Cognate with {{cog|pt|jazer}} and {{cog|es|yacer}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|gl|/ʃaˈθeɾ/}}
